### 1. One-Line Summary
* Nittaku G-1: A grippy, medium-hard “spin + high throw” ESN classic that rewards full strokes with heavy rotation and stability.
* NUZN 45: A modern controlled hybrid tensor (slightly tacky + medium sponge) aimed at easier spin access and precision for non-elite power levels.

