* **Speed & Gears:**
    * **Low Impact:**
        * Nittaku G-1: Needs a bit of commitment to wake up; stable but not “free speed.”
        * NUZN 45: Easier to engage at medium effort; more “help” in the sponge and topsheet for safe pace.
