        * NUZN 45: High spin potential, but its “selling point” is more consistent access than absolute maximum. :contentReference[oaicite:7]{index=7}
    * **Topsheet Grip:**
        * Nittaku G-1: Very grippy, non-tacky style (classic ESN grip). :contentReference[oaicite:8]{index=8}
