* **Flight Path (Throw Angle):**
    * **Arc Height:**
        * Nittaku G-1: Generally higher throw and naturally arcing topspin trajectory. :contentReference[oaicite:10]{index=10}
        * NUZN 45: Medium-to-medium-high arc; a bit flatter than “very high throw” rubbers when driven forward.
    * **Safety:**
        * Nittaku G-1: High net clearance on loops; strong safety window in topspin exchanges. :contentReference[oaicite:11]{index=11}
        * NUZN 45: High safety through grip + controllable sponge; especially forgiving when the contact point is slightly late. :contentReference[oaicite:12]{index=12}

* **Feel & Feedback:**
