* **Blocking & Countering:**
    * **Passive Block:**
        * Nittaku G-1: Very stable on compact blocks; firm sponge resists bottoming out.
        * NUZN 45: Softer sponge can absorb well; may require a touch more angle discipline against very fast topspin.
    * **Active Counter:**
        * Nittaku G-1: Strong for counter-topspin when you accelerate; high arc helps over-the-table counters. :contentReference[oaicite:17]{index=17}
